        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Ammunition</strong> Arrow</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This arrow splits at the far end of the shaft into five branching arrowheads, making it impractical for single targets but deadly in combat. When you fire an activated <em>enfilading arrow</em>, it sails upward and shatters into countless copies. The arrows then rain down in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] at any point within your weapon's first range increment, dealing [[/r {6d8}[piercing]]]{6d8 piercing damage} to all creatures in the area (@Check[type:reflex|dc:25|basic:true|traits:ammunition|showDC:all]).</p>\n<p>If a creature critically fails the save and you have access to the bow critical specialization effect, the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized} and must spend an Interact action to attempt a @Check[type:athletics|dc:10|name:Pull Free of Pinning Arrow|traits:ammunition|showDC:all] check to pull the missile free; it can't move from its space until it succeeds.</p>"
